graph TD
    Client([User/Browser])
    
    subgraph GitHub Pages Hosting
        Frontend[Frontend: index.html / CSS / JS]
    end

    subgraph Render.com Compute Node
        Backend[Backend API: Node.js]
    end
    
    subgraph Supabase Cloud
        DB[(PostgreSQL DB: Metrics)]
        Storage[Blob Storage: assets]
    end

    Client <-->|Loads Initial UI| Frontend
    Client -->|Cross-Origin API Fetch| Backend
    
    Backend -->|POST /visitors| DB
    Backend -->|GET /resume| Storage
    
    DB -.->|Returns count| Backend
    Storage -.->|Returns Public URL| Backend
    Backend -.->|Sends Metric / Redirect| Client
